'''Zen'''是一種[[x86-64|x86-64]][[微架構|微架構]]，由[[AMD|AMD]]開發，2016年發表，取代[[Bulldozer微架構|Bulldozer微架構]]及其改進版本。該微架構是AMD重返高效能運算市場的重要產品，與舊有架構相比幾乎完全重新設計並以新工藝製作以提升效能，同時還引入眾多新特性，處理器產品以[[SoC|SoC]]或半SoC形態面市。而首款Zen微架構的處理器，核心代號「Summit Ridge」，正式品牌名稱為「[[AMD_Ryzen|Ryzen]]」，而中文名稱為「銳龍」，于2017年3月2日正式上市。<ref name="zen_amd" /><ref name="AMD hints at high-performance Zen">{{cite news | url=http://www.bit-tech.net/news/hardware/2014/09/11/amd-zen/1 | publisher=bit-tech | title=AMD hints at high-performance Zen x86 architecture | date=11 September 2014 | accessdate=15 December 2014 | archive-date=2015-04-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402004804/http://www.bit-tech.net/news/hardware/2014/09/11/amd-zen/1 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="WCCF 2016 roadmap">{{cite web |last=Mujtaba |first=Hassan |url=http://wccftech.com/amd-announces-20142016-roadmap-20nm-project-skybridge-k12-64bit-arm-cores-2016/ |title=AMD Announces 2014-2016 Roadmap – 20nm Project SkyBridge and K12 64-bit ARM Cores For 2016 |publisher=WCCF Tech |date=May 5, 2014 |accessdate=January 15, 2015 |archive-date=2015-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310062319/http://wccftech.com/amd-announces-20142016-roadmap-20nm-project-skybridge-k12-64bit-arm-cores-2016/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AMD Ryzen - the Zen architecture release date, specs, price and rumours|url=https://www.pcgamesn.com/amd/amd-zen-release-date-specs-prices-rumours|website=PCGamesN|accessdate=2017-02-20|language=en|date=2017-02-14|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155203/https://www.pcgamesn.com/amd/amd-zen-release-date-specs-prices-rumours|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=AMD 開啟重返榮耀之旅，正式推出 Ryzen 處理器暨平台|url=http://www.techbang.com/posts/49682-returning-to-the-road-to-glory-amd-launched-ryzen-processor-and-the-platform?from=left_column|website=techbang.com|accessdate=2017-03-27|archive-date=2017-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170327173415/http://www.techbang.com/posts/49682-returning-to-the-road-to-glory-amd-launched-ryzen-processor-and-the-platform?from=left_column|dead-url=no}}</ref>外部合作方面，超微以2.93億美金賣給[[中科海光|中科海光]]的x86架構CPU使用，不過預計不會提供後續型號的授權<ref>{{cite web|title=中國海光 CPU 將在下一代採用 7nm 製程，預計可能於年底流片|url=https://news.xfastest.com/others/80508/china-hygon-cpu-will-use-7nm-next-gen/|access-date=2021-04-14|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417215612/https://news.xfastest.com/others/80508/china-hygon-cpu-will-use-7nm-next-gen/}}</ref>。

== 概覽 ==
首個基於Zen微架構的系統展示平台在2016年的[[E3电子娱乐展|E3消費電子展]]上現身，而架構的細節，則是到了同年[[英特爾開發者論壇|英特爾開發者論壇]]正舉行時，在其舉行地點對面的街區上公佈。不同於使用將近6年的並且在各種小修小補和僅更新了一次製作工藝的Bulldozer微架構，Zen微架構由曾經領隊設計K6/K7/K8架構、2012年回歸AMD的Jim Keller帶隊操刀另行開發，並且直接使用14nm節點FinFET製程，著重於提升每個CPU核心的效能，最初目標是比當時預期的[[Excavator微架構|Bulldozer微架構最終形態]]時{{le|每時鐘週期指令數|Instructions per cycle}}（IPC）高出40%。此外處理器連接界面、插座、記憶體支援等等都力圖更新到最新規格。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/3020184/computers/amd-zen-based-cpus-and-apus-will-unify-around-socket-am4.html|title=AMD Zen-based CPUs and APUs will unify around Socket AM4|date=8 January 2016|author=Brad Chacos|work=PCWorld|accessdate=2017-03-27|archive-date=2017-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202193557/http://www.pcworld.com/article/3020184/computers/amd-zen-based-cpus-and-apus-will-unify-around-socket-am4.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了效能和功能上的提升以外，還試圖以[[AMD_APU|AMD APU]]產品線的經驗將新架構系統平台的體積縮小，令單一一顆CPU可以以SoC形態出現並支援常見的[[匯流排|匯流排]]規格（包括[[PCIe|PCIe]]、[[SATA|SATA]]、[[USB|USB]]等）。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/3124306/hardware/dont-call-amds-upcoming-zen-chip-a-cpu.html|title=How AMD's powerful Zen chip flouts the SoC stereotype|work=PCWorld|access-date=2017-03-08|language=en|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206161943/http://www.pcworld.com/article/3124306/hardware/dont-call-amds-upcoming-zen-chip-a-cpu.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Cutress|first1=Ian|title=Early AMD Zen Server CPU and Motherboard Details|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/10581/early-amd-zen-server-cpu-and-motherboard-details-codename-naples-32cores-dual-socket-platforms-q2-2017|accessdate=22 March 2017|publisher=Anandtech|date=18 August 2016|archive-date=2017-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322111447/http://www.anandtech.com/show/10581/early-amd-zen-server-cpu-and-motherboard-details-codename-naples-32cores-dual-socket-platforms-q2-2017|dead-url=no}}</ref>加之此前發表的300系列晶片組、[[Socket_AM4|Socket AM4]]/Socket FP4插座、對[[DDR4|DDR4]]的支援等，這些使得AMD可以令Zen微架構只需些少修改即可涵蓋當前的[[筆電|筆電]]、小尺寸[[個人電腦|PC]]乃至[[桌上型電腦|桌上型電腦]]、[[工作站|工作站]]、[[伺服器|伺服器]]（特別是高運算密度的雲端運算平台）等運算系統平台。<ref>{{cite web|title=AMD’s Zen Processor Might Power Next-Generation Apple MacBook Pro – Custom SOC Design With HBM2 Memory System|url=http://wccftech.com/amd-zen-soc-apple-macbook-pro/|website=wccftech.com|accessdate=2017-03-30|archive-date=2017-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330174143/http://wccftech.com/amd-zen-soc-apple-macbook-pro/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://digi.tech.qq.com/a/20150223/004315.htm |title = AMD Zen架构处理器明年问世 性能媲美Skylake |author = 郑双艳 |date = 2015-02-23 |publisher = 騰訊數碼 |language = zh-cn |accessdate = 2015-02-24 |quote = 另外，在封装接口方面，Zen架构将会实现与现有ARM处理器的接口兼容和互换。AMD在去年发布ARM架构处理器时就宣称将与以后的处理器实现接口的兼容，看来AMD是早有准备。而如果这一技术能够实现，那么对于企业级用户来说，这将是一个巨大的进步，对ARM阵营也将是一个强心剂。 |archive-date = 2015-02-23 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150223213943/http://digi.tech.qq.com/a/20150223/004315.htm |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="14nm AMD Zen CPU Will Have DDR4 and Simultaneous Multithreading">{{cite news | url=http://news.softpedia.com/news/14nm-AMD-Zen-CPU-Will-Have-DDR4-and-Simultaneous-Multithreading-471401.shtml | publisher=Softpedia | title=14nm AMD Zen CPU Will Have DDR4 and Simultaneous Multithreading | date=28 January 2015 | accessdate=31 January 2015 | archive-date=2015-03-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150310042615/http://news.softpedia.com/news/14nm-AMD-Zen-CPU-Will-Have-DDR4-and-Simultaneous-Multithreading-471401.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>2017年中發表的AMD Epyc系列，取代Opteron成為AMD面向企業應用（特別是[[雲端運算|雲端運算]]）的企業級CPU系列，並且可作為無需[[南橋晶片|南橋晶片]]的半SoC化產品。<ref name="twtn">{{cite web|title=【x86 興衰史】為何 AMD 在 x86 CPU 被 Intel 壓著打整整 10 年？戰況會改觀嗎？|url=https://technews.tw/2017/07/28/intel-vs-amd-history-of-x86-cpu/|website=TechNews 科技新報|accessdate=2017-08-25|archive-date=2017-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170825193454/https://technews.tw/2017/07/28/intel-vs-amd-history-of-x86-cpu