=== 改進之處 === 
Zen+微架構的處理器使用了[[GlobalFoundries|GlobalFoundries]]的「12奈米」LP（Leading Performance）工藝製作，<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.extremetech.com/computing/256213-amd-will-use-new-globalfoundries-12nm-node-future-cpus-gpus|title=AMD Will Use 'New' GlobalFoundries 12nm Node for Future CPUs, GPUs|last=|first=|date=2017-09-22|work=ExtremeTech|access-date=2018-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180205001142/https://www.extremetech.com/computing/256213-amd-will-use-new-globalfoundries-12nm-node-future-cpus-gpus|archive-date=2018-02-05|dead-url=no|language=en-US}}</ref>該製程工藝實際上是同廠[[14奈米製程|14奈米]]LPP工藝的改良版，重在提高單位面積下電晶體的數量（即同等電路下減少晶片面積），而Zen+相較於Zen而言沒有大變動，電晶體數量也是幾乎一樣。<ref name='AT_dd'>{{cite news|last1=Cutress|first1=Ian|title=The AMD 2nd Gen Ryzen Deep Dive|url=https://www.anandtech.com/show/12625/amd-second-generation-ryzen-7-2700x-2700-ryzen-5-2600x-2600|accessdate=30 April 2018|publisher=Anandtech|date=19 April 2018|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612210509/https://www.anandtech.com/show/12625/amd-second-generation-ryzen-7-2700x-2700-ryzen-5-2600x-2600|dead-url=yes}}</ref>有第三方媒體對基於Zen+的Ryzen 7進行實測，發現除了晶片面積有所減少以外，相較於第一代也有小幅的時脈提升及同等效能下功耗的下降，<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kampman|first1=Jeff|title=AMD lays out its Ryzen and Radeon plans for 2018 and beyond at CES|url=https://techreport.com/review/33046/amd-lays-out-its-ryzen-and-radeon-plans-for-2018-and-beyond-at-ces/|accessdate=8 January 2018|publisher=Tech Report|date=8 January 2018|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613014632/https://techreport.com/review/33046/amd-lays-out-its-ryzen-and-radeon-plans-for-2018-and-beyond-at-ces|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name='AT_dd' />但這個也與AMD對Zen的電源管理有改善有關，主要是對AMD SenseMI電源管理的調整改善，令CPU電源管理模組更快響應CPU的負荷需要，並且在有負荷時CPU核心的時脈比此前Zen的更能維持高[[時脈|時脈]]，特別是XFR2，還進一步改進了檢測單個CPU核心在當前最高工作溫度下的最高時脈的特性。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Leather|first1=Anthony|title=AMD Confirms New Zen+ Ryzen CPUs For April 2018: X470 Chipset, Threadripper And APUs Inbound Too|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/antonyleather/2018/01/07/amd-confirms-new-zen-ryzen-cpus-for-april-2018-x470-chipset-threadripper-and-apus-inbound-too|accessdate=9 January 2018|publisher=Forbes|date=7 January 2018|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612211734/https://www.forbes.com/sites/antonyleather/2018/01/07/amd-confirms-new-zen-ryzen-cpus-for-april-2018-x470-chipset-threadripper-and-apus-inbound-too|dead-url=no}}</ref>

除了換用更新的製程以及對CPU電源管理的改善外，還有：<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mah Ung|first1=Gordon|title=AMD reveals Ryzen 2, Threadripper 2, 7nm Navi, and more in CES blockbuster|url=https://www.pcworld.com/article/3246211/computers/amd-reveals-ryzen-2-threadripper-2-7nm-navi-and-more-in-ces-blockbuster.html|accessdate=9 January 2018|publisher=PC World|date=7 January 2018|archive-date=2018-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180113113011/https://www.pcworld.com/article/3246211/computers/amd-reveals-ryzen-2-threadripper-2-7nm-navi-and-more-in-ces-blockbuster.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 降低對[[CPU快取|快取]]、記憶體存取時所需的時鐘週期
* 提升快取頻寬
* 更佳的記憶體相容性以及更高效能參數的記憶體支援（原生支援DDR4-2933，XMP/AMP支援下更達DDR4-3400+）

這些改進使得Zen+相較於Zen而言同時脈下每時鐘週期能處理多3%的指令數量，最高時脈也有6%的提升，最終大約取得10%左右的效能提升。<ref name='AT_dd' />

配套的晶片組更新至[[AMD_Fusion_Controller_Hub#400系列|400系列]]，不過原先300系列的通過AGESA EFI韌體更新後（若廠商提供）也可以使用基於Zen+的處理器。
